parameters: The princess enters the city of Leonis, which sits at
the center of her kingdom. One of the most prosperous
cities of Karaina, it enjoys the protection of the
royal guard itself, acting as the capitol city of
the realm. Want me to give you the guided tour?

this establishment provides the best service in the
country, at an affordable price, showing the
generosity of the kingdom.

CAM 25 31
Next, the item and equipment shops. Fairly humble,
due to the lack of requirements for such an outlet,
the kingdom has been at peace for so long, the sale
of weapons has deteriorated, other than for people
taking up hunting the local monster population, but
for the start of the princess' journey, it should
be more than enough.
CAM 31 29
The tavern, a source of information and rumours.
Even though the princess is royalty, she's still not
old enough to drink here, but the denizens will still
be kind enough to share information, quests, or even
occasionally give gifts and offerings, it's still
worth a visit.
CAM 19 7
And the last thing of note is the Quite Honourable
Guild branch, a hub for adventurers around the world.
It's always a good idea to visit here to pick up
quests, and if you're struggling or lonely out in
the field, you can hire adventurers here to join
your party.
